data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with 1 car detached garage and carport. Spacious main floor master suite and open floor plan with vaulted ceilings make this home feel open and large. There is an office/bonus room that could be a non-conforming bedroom if you need 4! Conveniently located between Bonners Ferry and Sandpoint with easy access.
